OL,6,FHis father was also ordered to pay #85
OL,7,Fcosts and #200 compensation to
OL,8,FSouthport Mosque.
OL,10,FThe boy, who the court was told had no
OL,11,Fprevious convictions and has had a
OL,12,Fdifficult home life, cannot be
OL,13,Fidentified because of his age.
OL,15,FJudge Lloyd told him: "These offences
OL,16,Fhave shaken society to the core. It
OL,17,Fwas an angry mob and you chose to be
OL,18,Fpart of it.
OL,20,F"You have had a complicated and in
OL,21,Fmany ways sad young life.
