OL,6,F"But what you did that night was very
OL,7,Fwrong. It really was a horrible
OL,8,Fsituation and you made it more
OL,9,Fhorrible by engaging in throwing
OL,10,Fstones.
OL,12,F"Many police officers were hurt that
OL,13,Fnight."
OL,15,FPc Bourhill of Merseyside Police said
OL,16,Fhe was part of patrol at around 7.45pm
OL,17,Fon 31 July when he noticed a small
OL,18,Fgathering of people near the mosque
OL,19,Fgrowing in size.
