OL,6,FHe said missiles soon began to be
OL,7,Fthrown at the mosque and the police,
OL,8,Fwith some in the crowd pushing
OL,9,Fofficers and saying: "Why are you
OL,10,Fprotecting them?"
OL,12,FAs bricks were thrown officers donned
OL,13,Friot gear and shields to keep the mob
OL,14,Ffrom storming the mosque.
OL,16,FCCTV shown to the court showed a
OL,17,Fpolice van was set on fire during
OL,18,Fhours of disorder involving hundreds
OL,19,Fof people.
