OL,6,FPc Bourhill was hit on the chin by a
OL,7,Fpiece of concrete, leaving him
OL,8,Fbleeding, then hit on the head by a
OL,9,Fsecond concrete missile, causing him
OL,10,Fto black out before being taken to
OL,11,Fhospital, the court heard.
OL,13,FHe said in a statement: "I have never
OL,14,Fexperienced such high level of
OL,15,Fviolence towards police."
OL,17,FIn all 93 police officers were injured
OL,18,Fin the trouble.
