OL,6,FIbrahim Hussein, chairman of Southport
OL,7,FIslamic Society Mosque, said in a
OL,8,Fstatement that after the stabbings
OL,9,Fthree security guards turned up at the
OL,10,Fmosque, sent by the Home Office.
OL,12,FThe next day he was made aware of
OL,13,Fsocial media "lies spread to create
OL,14,Fhate", which claimed the girls' killer
OL,15,Fwas a man named Ali who was an
OL,16,Fimmigrant and attended the mosque.
