OL,6,FThat evening a crowd began to gather
OL,7,Foutside the mosque shouting "We will
OL,8,Fget you out of here, you Muslim
OL,9,Fbastards", before empty lager cans
OL,10,Fwere thrown at the building, Mr
OL,11,FHussein's statement added.
OL,13,FHe said he locked himself and a small
OL,14,Fnumber of worshippers inside the
OL,15,Fmosque as bricks were hurled at the
OL,16,Fbuilding.
