OL,3,CBoy, 12, becomes youngest to be
OL,4,Csentenced for Southport riots
OL,6,FMr Hussein said he looked at the CCTV
OL,7,Fmonitor and could see 500 to 1,000
OL,8,Fpeople outside, and became "very
OL,9,Fscared and worried", with one young
OL,10,Fman "shaking in fear".
OL,12,FDespite the mob outside, the
OL,13,Fworshippers continued praying and
OL,14,Fcalled police, who said officers were
OL,15,Fon the way, but Mr Hussein was asked
OL,16,Fto stay on the line before riot police
OL,17,Farrived.
OL,19,FThe building began heating up with
OL,20,Fsmoke inside as a police van outside
OL,21,Fwas torched by the mob.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@SO]rD@EOUrD@UO]
