OL,6,FMr Hussein said he was escorted from
OL,7,Fthe building by officers at midnight
OL,8,Fand outside looked like a "war zone".
OL,10,FHe returned the next day to find
OL,11,Fcouncil workers, the fire brigade and
OL,12,Flocal residents clearing up.
OL,14,FThe mosque walls, broken windows and
OL,15,Ffences were repaired by local building
OL,16,Ffirms without charge.
OL,18,FMr Hussein added: "The community have
OL,19,Fbeen very supportive. I would describe
OL,20,Fthem as in shock."
