OL,6,FHeather Toohey, defending, said that
OL,7,Fin terms of having an unstable
OL,8,Fupbringing, the youngster "ticks every
OL,9,Fbox".
OL,11,FShe said he simply got "caught up" in
OL,12,Fthe trouble, adding: "He knows he
OL,13,Facted out of stupidity."
